parameters:
\SE[29]Y-You're right, it's weird after all...! \SE[57]It's
strange at a time like this...!

\SE[62]But... I also thought about it a little. Dying in the
dream of the person I love so much... \SE[43]It's kind of
romantic, don't you think...

\SE[79]You understand...!? \.No way, \SE[22]I'm so happy that
tears are coming out...!
\SE[63]Geez, don't make me laugh... I let my guard down...
\SE[43]But, thank you... \SE[55]I might not feel anxious anymore.
\SE[59]Can you... \SE[56]keep me locked inside of you?

\SE[45]... Yes, I will keep you locked inside. \SE[31] Forever in
this world, just you and me... \SE[30] I will never let you go.
\SE[45]Ahaha... If Lunaroa says so, then I feel relieved...

\SE[61]But still... I'm a little scared. \SE[25]Will you stay by
my side forever...?

\SE[46]It's not obvious at all. If you're not with me...
\SE[45]My life up until now would have been meaningless.

\SE[27]You know... when Luna is nearby, I can't help but smile,
and tears start to well up... \SE[25]...I feel so relieved.

\SE[46]That's... I feel the same way. \.Hehe, we're on the same
page, huh? \SE[30]

\SE[25]At the end... I'm glad we could spend time together.
\SE[56]I'm glad I love you.
Thank you... I love you... Luna...

\SE[0]Hmm... This is also a happy ending, right?... \SE[16]In the
end, being together with the person you love... \SE[15]This is
what they call a maiden's dream feeling...

\SE[32]There are also closure moments like that, right?
\SE[30]Yeah, yeah, that's also a form of diversity....
\SE[2]Laura... Me? \SE[4]There's something I want to tell you...
\SE[29]\SM[pop] I hate this kind of thing!!

\SE[9]What should I say... It's like... \.It's different from the
happiness I wanted to see...! \!\SE[23]It's too perverse for
me... \!\SE[24]Or maybe it's just too mature... Mmm...

\SE[52]I prefer the feeling of ordinary happiness more.
\SE[32]Spending peaceful and harmonious everyday life together...
\SE[30]And eventually, maybe even having children together...

\SE\SE[15]While watching the growth of our children... \SE[15]As
we grow old, the two of us confirm our happiness together.
\SE[16]Even if we lose the radiance of youth, we still have the
warmth of our family....

\SE[14]I wanted to see that! \SE[13]What...! Both of us feeling a
romantic connection to a double suicide, it's a bit too mature,
isn't it...!

\SE[16]Ahaha... That's right...! It seems like the two of us are
determined to die...

\SE[0]Let me forcefully show you ordinary happiness and save you!
\!\SE[1]If that's the case, you have no choice but to become
happy...!

\SE[2]Hmm... Enough for two people, huh.... \SE[38]It's a bit too
much, but I guess it can't be helped....

\SE[14]Ugh... It's so heavy for both of us...! \SE[23]Making
children work like this... It's a crime...!

\SE[16]Alright, this should do it...! \.I can just throw it
randomly, right?!
